column2:
eie %>%
  mutate(implementing_partner = str_sub(implementing_partner, end = 50L), 
         indicator_number = paste0("indicator", parse_number(indicator_short))) %>%
  select(county, adm1_pcode, implementing_partner, indicator_number, total_reached) %>% 
  
  pivot_wider(names_from = indicator_number, values_from = total_reached) %>%  
  select(indicator1, indicator2, indicator3, indicator4, indicator5, indicator6) %>% 
  map_depth(., 2, ~ifelse(is.null(.x), 0, .x), .ragged = TRUE)
